msgid "Scenario III: Return to Echoes of the Past"
msgstr "冒险III：重返往事回声"

msgid "Randomly choose one [[Basement]] Historical Society location, one [[Ground Floor]] Historical Society location, one [[Second Floor]] Historical Society location, and one [[Third Floor]] Historical Society location. Remove those locations from the game, without looking at their revealed sides."
msgstr "随机选择一个[[地下室]]历史协会地点，一个[[一楼]]历史协会地点，一个[[二楼]]历史协会地点，还有一个[[三楼]]历史协会地点。将这些地点移出游戏，不要查看它们的已揭示面。"

msgid "Put the following locations into play: Entry Hall, all three copies of Quiet Halls, and the remaining 8 Historical Society locations. Each investigator begins play in the Entry Hall."
msgstr "将以下地点放置入场：入口大厅，全部3张宁静的走廊，剩下的8个历史协会地点。每位调查员从入口大厅开始游戏。"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: Hidden Library, Possessed Oathspeaker, Mr. Peabody, The Tattered Cloak, Clasp of Black Onyx, and both Keeper of the Oath enemies."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于游戏场外：隐藏的图书馆，附身宣誓者，皮博迪先生，槛褛披风，黑玛瑙扣环，2张监誓者敌人。"

msgid ""
"For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rule applies:\n"
"\"<b>Forced</b> - After the investigators advance to act 2 or act 3: Spawn a set-aside Keeper of the Oath in any empty Historical Society location.\"\n"
"Attach the Return to Echoes of the Past scenario reference card to the scenario reference card as a reminder."
msgstr ""
"在本场冒险接下来的时间里，增加以下额外规则：\n"
"“<b>强制</b> - 在调查员推进至场景2或场景3后：在任意无人的历史协会地点生成一张放在一边的监誓者。”\n"
"将本卡牌叠加到冒险辅助卡，以作提示。"
